          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1971.-step-3-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, dissolve the <strong>chipotle paste</strong> (can't handle the heat? Go easy!) and <strong>tomato paste</strong> in 100ml <span class=\"text-danger\">[150ml]</span> <strong>boiled water</strong> – this is your <strong>spicy stock</strong></p>\n<p>Once fragrant, add the <strong>spicy stock</strong> to the pan with the<strong> soy sauce</strong> and cook for 2-3 min further or until the sauce has thickened – this is your <strong>chipotle pulled pork</strong> </p>",
      "order": 4,
